<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><span style="line-height: 17.12px;"><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br><span style="background-color: white;">We are writing to let you know that your insurance will be automatically renewed on DD/MM/YEAR.<br></span></span></span></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Your renewal will be&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">based on the information you provided last year</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;and your official renewal&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">quotation will follow within the next 14 days</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If any of your circumstances or requirements have changed since you last purchased your insurance, or you have made a claim or are aware of any circumstances that might lead to a claim, please call our&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Client Services Team</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;so they can make any necessary amendments and reissue a renewal quotation.</span><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b style="font-size: large;">Your renewal payment</b><font size="4"><b><br></b></font></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Payment will be taken using the same method and details you provided last year. If you would like to change these please contact us on the number above.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>If you pay by direct debit&nbsp;</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">- Your first direct debit for your renewal will be requested up to 10 days prior to your renewal, but will not be taken until your renewal date.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>If you pay by debit/credit card&nbsp;</b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Payment will be collected on or around 5 days before your renewal date and can take a few days to clear.</span><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b style="font-size: large;">Why renew with Kingsbridge?</b></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Up to £2,500 tools and equipment cover</b>&nbsp;included as standard at no extra cost (with up to £20k worth of cover available to purchase).</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Next business day payout on accepted tool theft claims</b>, helping to get Britain's tradespeople back on the job faster.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Nil excess and no hidden fees</b>&nbsp;on most professions covered, reducing out-of-pocket or unexpected costs.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>UK-based in-house specialists</b>, including easy, quick access to brokers, and rapid, responsive claims processing managed by a dedicated claims team.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>All core covers in one place</b>, wrapped into a single neat, affordable package attached to one easy payment.</font></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you have any questions regarding your renewal or the information above, please don't hesitate to get in touch on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>. We look forward to another year together.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>